These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, garlic, lettuce, pumpkin, radish
City: liverpool, paris, prague, edinburgh, new-york
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is in the middle##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to prague##2
6. the person eating radish is in the middle##1
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Food          | garlic | cauliflower | radish | pumpkin | lettuce |
| City   | prague  | new-york      | edinburgh   | liverpool     | paris    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, crime, action, family, thriller
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, surfing, swimming, tennis
1. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person watching action movies and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
7. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | family       | thriller    | mystery | crime   |
| Sport      | snowboarding | badminton | swimming | tennis      | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different nationalities: british, polish, thai, italian, chinese
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, electronic, metal, reggae, trance
1. the fan of reggae is the british##1
2. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of metal##1
4. the polish is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
5. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
6. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
7. the thai is on the right of the british##1
8. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Nationality         | british | thai | polish | italian    | chinese |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | blues        | metal      | electronic | trance      |

