.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, puzzles, rock-climbing, sudoku, woodworking
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, bike, ship, airplane, bus
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the bike##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person driving the ship and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
7. the person driving the bus is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Hobby         | chess      | sudoku | rock-climbing | puzzles   | woodworking  |
| Transport   | airplane | bus    | ship        | jet-ski | bike |

