.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, mirinda, soy-milk, tea
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, soul, blues, hip-hop, salsa
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
5. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | tea      | lemonade | iced-tea   | soy-milk  | mirinda  |
| Music-Genre   | blues | hip-hop | punk | soul | salsa |

