.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, lemonade, mirinda, tea
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, bike, bus, train, tram
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the tram and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person driving the bus is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
8. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Beverage   | cola        | 7up                | mirinda  | lemonade  | tea            |
| Transport        | airplane | tram | bike | bus | train |

