.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, milk, sprite, water
5 different pets are kept: turtle, ferret, goldfish, guinea-pig, bird
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
8. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Beverage   | water       | milk   | lemonade    | sprite    | hot-chocolate |
| Pet        | goldfish | turtle | ferret | bird | guinea-pig     |

