.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: mauve, grey, brown, coral, green
5 different pets are kept: fish, goat, guinea-pig, horse, pony
1. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes coral is the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the horse is the person who likes coral##1
4. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes grey is the owner of the fish##1
6. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes grey and the person who likes mauve##2
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
8. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Color   | green | grey | brown     | mauve | coral |
| Pet           | goat | fish     | guinea-pig | pony    | horse      |

