The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, drama, thriller, romance, time-travel
1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
3. the person eating broccoli is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching drama movies##2
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is the person eating pepper##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Food    | garlic    | spinach  | broccoli      | radish     | pepper |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | drama | romance | thriller | time-travel |

