.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
There 5 different types of food: lime, orange, pineapple, plum, pumpkin
There are 5 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda, almond-milk, 7up, iced-tea
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating lime##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
4. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating orange##2
7. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Food        | plum | pumpkin | lime  | pineapple | orange     |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | almond-milk     | iced-tea | sprite      | 7up |

