.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, sprite, almond-milk, milk
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, chess, dancing, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person drinking iced-tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | milk   | almond-milk  | iced-tea     | water | sprite |
| Hobby   | board-games | dancing | woodworking | traveling | chess      |

