.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bolivar, dunhill, siglo, havana
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, dutch, italian, nigerian, thai
1. the siglo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the italian is the italian##1
3. the nigerian is on the far left##1
4. the australian is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
5. the havana-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the thai##2
6. the dutch is between the siglo-smoker and the thai##2
7. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
8. the thai is the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Cigar         | siglo | dunhill | bolivar | havana | davidoff     |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | dutch   | thai       | italian | australian |

