.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
5 different pets are kept: pony, lizard, bird, goat, dog
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, snowmobile, taxi, train
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the train and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is the owner of the pony##1
7. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Pet   | pony | bird      | goat | dog     | lizard      |
| Transport     | train | quad-bike | taxi | airplane | snowmobile |

 